ur Legacy</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Verde are a diverse and formidable force. Battle through hordes of enemies and destroy all threats that may come to your home world. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Feature</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 2D Side-scrolling starship maneuver. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 100+ unique weapons, each can be modified with 40+ different Tune-Ups. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 120+ Power-up in form of recruitment. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 20+ Core ships with diverse twist and playstyles.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Combat against 50 types of enemies, elites, high-threats and catastrophic level foes.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 6 Levels of challenge</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect resource and rescue survivors to rebuild your lost civilization.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Expand your new colony and unlock new research.</p></li></ul>",
